<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Al-Sadaq</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #007b3e;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #007b3e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007b3e;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #777777;
            font-size: 14px;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007b3e;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="100%" style="background-color:#f4f4f4;">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="600" class="email-container">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="header" align="center" style="background-color:#007b3e; padding: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
                            <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" alt="Al-Sadaq Logo" style="max-width:150px; height:auto;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="content" style="padding: 30px 20px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6;">
                            <h1 style="font-size: 28px; color: #007b3e; margin-bottom: 20px;">Welcome to Al-Sadaq!</h1>
                            <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
                            <p>We are delighted to welcome you to <b>Al-Sadaq</b>, a platform committed to supporting humanitarian efforts in Palestine and raising awareness through impactful campaigns.</p>
                            <p>Your account has been successfully created, and we&apos;ve generated a secure password for you to access your account.</p>
                            <p><b>Your Account Details:</b></p>
                            <p><b>Username:</b> <%= userEmail %></p>
                            <p><b>Password:</b> <%= userPassword %></p>
                            <p>For your security, we recommend that you change your password after logging in for the first time. To get started, click the button below:</p>
                            <p style="text-align: center;">
                                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button" style="display:inline-block; background-color:#007b3e; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; padding:15px 25px; border-radius:5px; font-size:16px; margin:20px 0; text-align:center;">Login to Your Account</a>
                            </p>
                            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don&apos;t hesitate to reach out to our support team at <%= supportEmail %>.</p>
                            <p>Thank you for joining us in our mission to create change and support the Palestinian cause. Together, we can make a difference.</p>
                            <p>Best regards,<br>The Al-Sadaq Team</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="footer" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #777777; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f8f8f8; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
                            <p>&copy; 2024 Al-Sadaq, All Rights Reserved.</p>
                            <p><a href="<%= websiteUrl %>" style="color: #007b3e; text-decoration: none;">Visit our website</a></p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
